<P>
   With MEXICO-Y2K-0101 _ OAXACA CITY, Mexico _ In this hemispheric
linchpin of Catholicism, the dawning of a new millennium .
Developing. (Contreras, Special to the Cox News Service).
</P>
<P>
   (EDs: Moving shortly after midnight EST. A 1STLD will move at
about 1:30 a.m. EST.)
</P>
