<SLUG> BC-MILLENNIUM-COMMENTARY-BOS </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
LOOKING AHEAD, LEAVING BEHIND 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  
 By DAVID M. SHRIBMAN  
 c.2000 The Boston Globe  
 
<TEXT>
<P>
   Let it be proclaimed: This morning, this simple winter morning,
represents more than the beginning of a new age. It represents an
