   &UR; FINANCIAL (f) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   STOCKS (Undated) _ U.S. stocks end at record highs, capping a
year of stellar gains on Wall Street, led by the New Economy's
white-hot technology shares. Records are set in all major indices
during an abbreviated day in observance of New Year's Eve. By
Kimberly Blanton. 700 words.
