June Powered by new 3.5-liter engine, Plano's Greg Ray drives to
victory in IRL Longhorn 500 at TMS ... Tiger Woods wins U.S. Open
golf title by five strokes at Pebble Beach, Calif. ... Despite
missing 18 of 20 free throws in final game, Shaquille O'Neal leads
Los Angeles Lakers over Indiana Pacers for NBA title ... Dedicating
their playoff run to ill coach Roger Neilson, Philadelphia Flyers
