earn Christmas Day date in Oahu Bowl opposite UCLA. Frogs finish
No. 11 in final polls.
December Kansas State defeats Oklahoma for Big 12 football title
... Virginia Tech QB Michael Vick wins Heisman Trophy. TCU running
