<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-Y2K-CZAR-2NDLD-WRITETHRU-HNS </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;     Y2K BUG HAS NO BITE IN THE NEW YEAR _ BUT SOME SLOT MACHINES GO
BAD 
</HEADLINE>
   &HT;     (EDS: Refiling to correct slug)  
 &HT;     (For use by New York Times News Service clients.)  
 &HT;     By JENNIFER CORBETT DOOREN  
 &HT;     c.1999 Hearst Newspapers  
