his recent turn as a double-dealing politician in the film ``Cradle
Will Rock.'' Currently, he is starring as Walter Franz, a damaged
businessman looking for emotional solace in the current Broadway
production of Arthur Miller's drama ``The Price.'' (Sara
Krulwich/The New York Times) LITE
