<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-12-31 23:31 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3875 &Cx1f; taf-z
u p BC-ADS-ASSESS-NYT &LR;      12-31 1133
